song.title: Pan-A-Sonic
song.info:
The song is named after a panasonic item (cannot remember what) .. either a battery, a keyboard or a walkman. I remember that it was very hot outside when I made this song. Nothing better to do than stay indoors :)
Features on Apathy's chart/musicdisk "Feedback #3" and was also supposed to be included on Rebels' unreleased musicdisk "Hybridslinky".
